    "ai-bv22:17.3_0": "you’d always give up everything,",
    "ai-bv22:17.4_0": "and their name is too small.",
    "ai-bv22:18.1_0": "Seeing the signs,",
    "ai-bv22:18.2_0": "I’m patching my elephant with horse;",
