    "ai-bv22:19.3_0": "today, the great hero,",
    "ai-bv22:19.4_0": "in the deer park at Makhādeva Mango Grove.",
    "ai-bv22:20.1_0": "conqueror of all and fraud,",
    "ai-bv22:20.2_0": "a disciple of the best,",
    "ai-bv22:20.3_0": "he is a sanctuary free of peril,",
    "ai-bv22:20.4_0": "Sikhī with the great hermit.",
    "ai-bv22:21.1_0": "And hairs grow in the ploughs,",
    "ai-bv22:21.2_0": "who had confidence.",
    "ai-bv22:21.3_0": "that Blessed One, the Buddha,",
    "ai-bv22:21.4_0": "a maiden is what is meant.",
    "ai-bv22:22.1_0": "Meanwhile, Nandaka,",
    "ai-bv22:22.2_0": "as well as the best sort,",
    "ai-bv22:22.3_0": "Your mind is pure and bright,",
    "ai-bv22:22.4_0": "He was attended on by the best.",
    "ai-bv22:23.1_0": "The Buddha is unexplained,",
    "ai-bv22:23.2_0": "excitement in the seventh time.",
    "ai-bv22:23.3_0": "My hair mown off, covered in mud,",
    "ai-bv22:23.4_0": "is the thirty-two marks of a great man.",
    "ai-bv22:24.1_0": "I was dispensationed by birth,",
    "ai-bv22:24.2_0": "who makes sure by day and night;",
    "ai-bv22:24.3_0": "look to the departed,",
    "ai-bv22:24.4_0": "it’s a league for three leagues.",
    "ai-bv22:25.1_0": "For seven years I wandered,",
    "ai-bv22:25.2_0": "that great hermit, great hero,",
    "ai-bv22:25.3_0": "Since he’s right,",
    "ai-bv22:25.4_0": "who attacked many men.",
    "ai-bv22:26.1_0": "I plunged into the teaching,",
    "ai-bv22:26.2_0": "and fulfilled in every case,",
    "ai-bv22:26.3_0": "Having hurting a sanctuary,",
    "ai-bv22:26.4_0": "I’m sorrowless, unstable.",
    "ai-bv22:27.1_0": "The direct route",
    "ai-bv22:27.2_0": "of the thirty-two marks of grass",
    "ai-bv22:27.3_0": "they’ve realized the Dhamma,",
    "ai-bv22:27.4_0": "but stilling all activities?",
    "ai-bv22:28.1_0": "the sage who has crossed over the world",
    "ai-bv22:28.2_0": "the non-ident of the unattached.",
    "ai-bv22:28.3_0": "Right there is a monument,",
    "ai-bv22:28.4_0": "as far as the league.”",
    "ai-bv22:29.1_0": "and twenty years of age."
